<!-- 定義與徵狀 Definition and symptoms -->
'''喉炎'''（Laryngitis）是描述[[喉|喉部]][[炎症|發炎]]的現象<ref name="BMJ2014">{{Cite journal|title=Laryngitis|url=http://www.bmj.com/content/bmj/349/bmj.g5827.full.pdf|last=Wood|first=John|last2=Athanasiadis|first2=Theodore|date=October 9, 2014|journal=The BMJ|publisher=The BMJ|issue=09|volume=331|last3=Allen|first3=Jacqui|access-date=September 25, 2016}}</ref>。[[喉|喉]]為人體主要的發聲構造，喉炎常見症狀包含[[聲音沙啞|聲音沙啞]]、[[发热|發燒]]、咳嗽、前頸疼痛，以及[[吞嚥困難|吞嚥困難]]<ref name="BMJ2014" /><ref name="PubMed2016">{{cite web|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0022339/|title=Laryngitis - National Library of Medicine|accessdate=9 November 2016|website=PubMed Health|archive-date=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910145257/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMHT0022339/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。症狀通常會持續兩周<ref name="BMJ2014" />。<!-- 病因 Causes -->

喉炎可按病程長短分為[[急性|急性]]及[[慢性病|慢性]]，通常症狀在三周以下我們稱為急性喉炎，反之則稱為慢性喉炎<!-- <ref name=BMJ2014/> -->。急性喉炎通常為病毒性[[上呼吸道感染|上呼吸道感染]]的症狀之一<!-- <ref name=BMJ2014/> -->，其他因素則可能包含喉部創傷（如咳嗽造成）或非病毒性病原體感染<ref name="BMJ2014" />。慢性喉炎則可能肇因於[[吸煙|吸煙]]、[[結核|結核]]病、[[过敏|过敏]]、[[胃食管反流病|胃食管反流病]]、[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]或[[结节病|结节病]]等等<ref name="BMJ2014" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Laryngitis: Types, Causes, and Treatments|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_otolaryngologic-clinics-of-north-america_2008-04_41_2/page/419|date=April 2008|journal=Otolaryngologic Clinics of North America|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.otc.2007.11.011|volume=41|pages=419–436|pmid=18328379|last1=Dworkin|first1=James Paul}}</ref>。這些因素都可能造成[[声带|声带]]的刺激<ref name="PubMed2016" />。<!-- 診斷 Diagnosis -->

如果合併有{{tsl|en|stridor|高頻喘鳴聲|高頻喘鳴聲}}、頸部[[放射線療法|放射線療法]]治療史、吞嚥困難，或症狀持續三周，或過去有抽菸，則必須進一步檢查<!-- <ref name=BMJ2014/> -->。若有影響到聲帶必須進行{{tsl|en|laryngoscopy|喉鏡|喉鏡}}檢查<!-- <ref name=BMJ2014/> -->。其他可能導致類似症狀的疾病有[[會厭炎|會厭炎]]、[[义膜性喉炎|义膜性喉炎]]、吸入{{tsl|en|foreign body|異物|異物}}或者[[喉癌|喉癌]]<ref name="BMJ2014" /><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA709|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2017: 5 Books in 1|date=2016|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323448383|page=709|language=en|last1=Ferri|first1=Fred F.|access-date=2017-03-13|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110105951/https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA709|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<!-- 治療與流行病學 Treatment and epidemiology -->

急性喉炎通常會自行痊癒<!-- <ref name=BMJ2014/> -->，減少聲帶使用和多喝水可能有幫助<ref name="BMJ2014" />。通常急性喉炎使用[[抗细菌药|抗細菌藥]]效果不大<ref name="Rev2015">{{cite journal|title=Antibiotics for acute laryngitis in adults.|last2=Cardona|first2=AF|date=23 May 2015|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD004783.pub5|volume=5|pages=CD004783|pmid=26002823|last1=Reveiz|first1=L}}</ref>。急性喉炎相較慢性喉炎常見許多<ref name="BMJ2014" />。慢性患者通常長發生於中年人，且男性比例高於女性<ref name="Dh2014">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=0ByMBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA292|title=Diseases of Ear, Nose and Throat|last2=Dhingra|first2=Shruti|date=2014|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9788131236932|edition=6|page=292|language=en|last1=Dhingra|first1=P. L.|access-date=2017-03-13|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110105828/https://books.google.ca/books?id=0ByMBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA292|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

